      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, the same blood analog fluid (glycerol-water, matched viscosity), and the same five operating points as the COU. Geometric scale factor is 1:1. Flow regime (Re, Womersley number) matches CPB clinical operating range. Validation domain is coincident with the COU domain.",
