      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second qualified CFD engineer not involved in the original setup (independent review checklist completed). Boundary condition assignments, material property inputs, and solver settings verified against the simulation plan document. No discrepancies found. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement of level 1.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
