        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Model inputs acceptance criteria",
        "description": "All model inputs must have a documented source (measurement, published database, or justified assumption). Uncertainty ranges must be defined for all inputs classified as influential by sensitivity analysis. Traceability to source documents must be maintained."
